PrecisAmendment to the LIVESTOCK CARCASS GRADING REGULATIONS modifying the current marking requirements for beef and lamb carcasses and ensuring that beef carcass markings reflect the greater emphasis on quality grade in the marketing of beef rather that the carcass yield class.
